24
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:52,340
Ah! Hold on! Hold on a minute!

25
00:02:53,190 --> 00:02:56,240
Wait for a moment! Wait! Are you okay, Pil?

26
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:59,180
- Please wait!
- Oh, what? Soo Jin!

27
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:01,940
