00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:48,210
Hey, I was looking at Oppa Dal Soo.

57
00:04:48,210 --> 00:04:52,190
You were just next to him.

58
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:56,780
Hey, long ago, when I first bumped into Oppa Dal Soo, who wore a red jacket,

