74
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:45,570
If you consider me the authentic brand, will you just leave me alone nicely?

75
00:05:45,570 --> 00:05:48,530
- In my house?
- What does it mean?

76
00:05:48,530 --> 00:05:50,230
