77
00:05:50,230 --> 00:05:54,770
I'm telling you I don't know why I'm here either! I mean it, Ahjussi!

78
00:05:54,770 --> 00:05:57,670
- Jin Sook! 
 - Seok Tae!

79
00:05:57,670 --> 00:06:00,190
Ahjussi, what are you doing here?

80
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:02,460
