85
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:17,270
- Thank goodness this person over here discovered them early on. 
- That's not it!

86
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:19,290
That's really not what it was!

87
00:06:19,290 --> 00:06:23,370
Guys, please listen to me. I really don't know why I'm here.

88
00:06:25,380 --> 00:06:30,450
It seemed these people made a ruckus because they were afraid that I might stop the Pil's treatment.

89
00:06:30,450 --> 00:06:33,120
This is Pil's friend and my employee.

90
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,950
So let's just settle this quietly and go home.

91
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:39,250
Even though you don't understand them, just think they are just  nonsense people.

92
00:06:39,250 --> 00:06:42,630
- Like this.
- Ahjumma, it's really not like that.

93
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:46,000
Dad! Dad, say something already! Come on!

94
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:50,350
I don't know why I'm here. I just opened my eyes and this is where I was.

95
00:06:50,350 --> 00:06:52,260
Darn it.

96
