106
00:07:24,570 --> 00:07:29,190
But where do you think Pil was trying to take his body?

107
00:07:29,190 --> 00:07:31,930
That was Seok Tae.

108
00:07:31,930 --> 00:07:34,950
Is everything okay with you?

109
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:38,280
That girl Soo Jin...

110
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:41,630
it seems like she recognized you.

111
00:07:41,630 --> 00:07:44,950
But is that even possible?

112
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:49,660
At any rate, you punk, what were doing acting romantic when you're in the midst of a crisis?

113
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:52,930
She was having such a hard time,

114
00:07:52,930 --> 00:07:55,920
I just wanted to try to comfort her a bit.

115
00:07:57,090 --> 00:08:01,530
If your son is up to no good, you, as his parent, should stop him.

116
00:08:01,530 --> 00:08:04,700
But instead of stopping him, you actually did it with him.

117
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:06,770
Does that make any sense?

118
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:11,770
It's not like I don't have inner energy (spirit) enough for being possessed by a ghost,

119
00:08:11,770 --> 00:08:13,490
but I'm positive that wasn't me.

120
00:08:13,490 --> 00:08:16,730
Stop talking about ghosts! You're really unbelievable.

121
00:08:16,730 --> 00:08:19,630
Have you no shame!

122
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:25,970
It looks like you always have a sense of rivalry when it comes to me.

123
00:08:25,970 --> 00:08:28,700
Let's not be involved in such an undesirable matter together in the future.

124
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:31,640
I have gone through a lot of things today.

125
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,800
I'll put up with you.

126
00:08:35,090 --> 00:08:37,250
Oh, by the way!

127
00:08:37,250 --> 00:08:41,060
Why aren't you delivering mail to my house?

128
00:08:41,060 --> 00:08:42,870
Did you think I wouldn't notice?

129
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:45,150
How childish.

130
00:08:50,590 --> 00:08:53,130
That wasn't me.

131
00:08:53,130 --> 00:08:56,600
I wasn't the one who did it. There's definitely something else to this.

132
00:08:56,600 --> 00:09:00,290
I feel some kind of wicked energy lurking around!

133
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:05,410
We were definitely drinking together, right?

134
00:09:05,410 --> 00:09:08,490
But I was tired so I closed my eyes for a bit,

135
00:09:08,490 --> 00:09:13,100
and when I woke up I was in Pil's hospital room.

136
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,490
Could it be alcohol-induced dementia?

137
00:09:14,490 --> 00:09:16,720
No, he's just an idiot, you dummy.

138
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:19,190
This, this... When he's drunk, there is no answer.

139
00:09:19,190 --> 00:09:20,970
Hey! Stop drinking, man!

140
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:24,770
That's not it, Hyung! I wasn't drunk! Really!

141
00:09:24,770 --> 00:09:27,770
But for some reason,

142
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:32,040
I feel like someone stole my body.

143
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:35,900
Damn it. I don't think I would take it if someone offered it to me.

144
00:09:38,090 --> 00:09:40,960
I feel weird.

145
00:09:42,190 --> 00:09:45,160
I've never missed the time for the manhole before,

146
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:47,660
but it can't be that missing it once means it's over, right?

147
00:09:47,660 --> 00:09:50,080
It will still work again, right?

148
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,930
How would I  know when someone who has used it before doesn't know?

149
00:09:53,930 --> 00:09:56,490
Time in my real time period is going to keep flowing as usual.

150
00:09:56,490 --> 00:09:58,990
Ugh, I don't have time for this.

151
00:09:58,990 --> 00:10:02,360
About Soo Jin's getting married or about the manhole...

152
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:07,100
I honestly don't understand what you're talking about, you punk.

153
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:13,390
I must go in the manhole tonight at midnight.

154
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:18,240
I have to travel through the manhole again and return everything  to normal.

155
00:10:24,780 --> 00:10:27,860
I think the two of us won't be enough.

156
00:10:27,860 --> 00:10:31,210
Let's bring one more person on our side.

157
00:10:31,210 --> 00:10:35,170
It was this, Sook. It's this right here.

158
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:40,040
This was the mirror where I saw Pil. He went from here to there in a flash.

159
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:43,560
- He went by in a flash just like that? 
- Yeah.

160
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,210
- Soo Jin.
 - Huh?

161
00:10:45,210 --> 00:10:48,560
- Do you hang out with people at all these days?
 - Nope.

162
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:51,790
Girl, you should go out and hang out with people.

163
00:10:51,790 --> 00:10:53,770
You used to have a lot of people around you in the past, right?

164
00:10:53,770 --> 00:10:56,360
But that's not the important thing though.

165
00:10:56,360 --> 00:11:00,470
