167
00:11:03,190 --> 00:11:06,910
Soo Jin, I can't go back home because of you.

168
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:09,250
You won't understand what I'm saying now.

169
00:11:09,250 --> 00:11:12,370
My eyes are capable of seeing Pil through it all.

170
00:11:12,370 --> 00:11:17,370
He really did go by in a flash from here to there and went out the door super fast.

171
00:11:17,370 --> 00:11:19,920
