172
00:11:23,590 --> 00:11:27,480
- Goo Gil.
 - Oh, no.

173
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:30,180
You go back in. I will take Jeong Ae first and I'll go home afterwards.

174
00:11:30,180 --> 00:11:33,530
I will take her home since you live out of the way anyway.

175
00:11:33,530 --> 00:11:34,710
I'll be fine since I closed up the shop already.

176
00:11:34,710 --> 00:11:36,820
You should open up the shop. You need that extra money.

177
00:11:36,820 --> 00:11:38,410
Why are you worrying about such things?

178
00:11:38,410 --> 00:11:40,520
You should go and do some cleaning ahead of time too.

179
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:44,990
Hey, stop it, you two! You should both leave. I will just go home by myself.

180
00:11:44,990 --> 00:11:46,620
You're going to go home by yourself?

181
00:11:46,620 --> 00:11:48,850
What?

182
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:55,200
No, how can you go home by yourself at this hour?

183
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:58,380
Hey. You take her home.

184
00:11:58,380 --> 00:12:01,160
You both haven't seen each other in a while so you guys should do some catching up as well.

185
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:03,390
No... I said I'd go home by myself.

186
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:07,230
Good idea. Let's get together tomorrow so we can talk more about Pil's situation.

187
00:12:07,230 --> 00:12:11,420
Tomorrow? I won't be able to tomorrow because I'm moving.

188
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:14,560
- I will be helping my mom, and it will be just us two moving.
 - Oh, yeah?

189
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:17,620
- You're moving?
 - It's getting late, so you guys should go already.

190
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:19,720
- Alright then. See you. 
 - No, you don't have to...

191
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:22,640
- Get in.
 - Bye, Jeong Ae.

192
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,520
