196
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:05,270
Oh my...

197
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:07,500
Don't do that.

198
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:26,070
You don't have to take me all the way home.

199
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:30,690
It's been a while. It's been six years since I've done this.

200
00:13:32,350 --> 00:13:35,710
It seems like you've changed a bit.

201
00:13:35,710 --> 00:13:39,180
People change, you know.

202
00:13:39,180 --> 00:13:44,210
Everything seemed too easy when I was younger, but I've realized that real life isn't that way.

203
00:13:44,210 --> 00:13:48,920
I can't believe I'm hearing you say stuff like that with your own mouth.

204
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:55,540
You... didn't miss me?

205
00:13:57,330 --> 00:14:01,030
Well... not really.

206
00:14:01,030 --> 00:14:05,470
I read in some book that women say things that are opposite of what they're really thinking.

207
00:14:05,470 --> 00:14:07,610
Are you still learning about dating through books?

208
00:14:07,610 --> 00:14:09,570
