209
00:14:09,570 --> 00:14:13,780
If I'm going to learn about women through women, then that means I have to meet some women.

210
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:16,350
But since I don't know any women, I end up not being able to meet with them.

211
00:14:16,350 --> 00:14:21,650
And because of that I'm not able to learn about women through women themselves so I never get to learn about them.

212
00:14:21,650 --> 00:14:26,750
Forget it. You make things way too complicated for no good reason.

213
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:44,200
You should go back in now.  That's your place right up there.

214
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,590
How did you know?

215
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:49,020
We passed by that place for the third time already.

216
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:50,680
Oh, yeah.

217
00:14:50,680 --> 00:14:52,280
I'm off now.

218
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:54,100
Okay.

