236
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:25,730
Do you think Soo Jin will choose you?

237
00:16:26,610 --> 00:16:28,530
Nobody knows that.

238
00:16:28,530 --> 00:16:32,700
Of course, when it comes to love, nobody knows how it will end.

239
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:36,790
Anyhow, you absolutely can't do that to Goo Gil. Do not possess him no matter what.

240
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:39,670
