00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:53,420
Wow. You're such a selfish man.

246
00:16:54,230 --> 00:16:56,640
Gosh darn it. Then who can I get to help me?

247
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:59,540
Power of love.

248
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:06,070
Why don't you believe in the power of love that goes beyond time and space?

249
00:17:09,790 --> 00:17:13,250
 Are you... able to see me? 

250
00:17:14,090 --> 00:17:16,090
 No. 

251
00:17:19,320 --> 00:17:21,630
 I can feel you. 

252
00:17:27,860 --> 00:17:30,460
Hey, I'm leaving.

253
00:17:32,980 --> 00:17:36,760
Hey, I said I'm leaving!

254
00:17:38,040 --> 00:17:41,810
Hey, open up your eyes properly, okay?

255
00:17:41,810 --> 00:17:45,360
Girl, you still can't believe me, huh?

256
00:17:46,730 --> 00:17:48,510
Do I look like a crazy person to you?

257
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:51,750
Yep, you look like a super crazy person.

258
00:17:53,290 --> 00:17:56,640
There is no way to explain this! There's none.

259
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:59,910
He appeared in front of me like this!

260
00:17:59,910 --> 00:18:05,550
Soo Jin, let's not think about anything tonight. You just try to get some good night sleep, alright?

261
00:18:05,550 --> 00:18:09,300
I will make you my bomb booze. Will you drink it and fall asleep?

262
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:14,530
Forget it. I'm really alright.

263
00:18:14,530 --> 00:18:18,590
Go do your job instead of worrying about me.

264
00:18:18,590 --> 00:18:23,170
I'm going to hurry and get some sleep so I can go see Pil tomorrow.

265
00:18:24,370 --> 00:18:28,510
Please do not go roaming around the streets like some crazy girl, okay?

266
00:18:28,510 --> 00:18:31,120
I'm going to tell your dad to guard you like a hawk before I leave, okay?

267
00:18:31,120 --> 00:18:35,200
Leave now! Call me, okay? Come visit me on the weekend.

268
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:37,930
Let's barbecue some meat.

269
00:18:37,930 --> 00:18:39,600
I'm off now.

270
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:41,880
Hurry up and leave so I can go to sleep.

271
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:44,630
- I'm leaving now.
 - Okay.

272
00:18:48,450 --> 00:18:50,980
I should get some sleep right away.

273
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:54,050
How is she?

274
00:18:54,050 --> 00:18:57,540
She was a bit strange earlier but I think she is fine now.

275
00:18:57,540 --> 00:19:00,810
She was strange earlier but she's better now?

276
00:19:00,810 --> 00:19:02,660
Could it be that something is really wrong with her?

277
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:05,460
Right! If she were strange, she should keep being strange.

278
00:19:05,460 --> 00:19:07,180
Or if she were fine, she should keep being fine.

279
00:19:07,180 --> 00:19:09,830
It's even weirder when a person changes constantly.

280
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:11,640
- There's something strange about this.
- Indeed there is!

281
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:16,080
Calm yourselves down so we won't end up crazy too.

282
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:20,480
It was a hard day for Soo Jin today so it's okay for her to act that way.

283
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:23,440
So all you have to do is watch over her the best you can.

284
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:27,120
- Okay. 
 - Alright, okay.

285
00:19:27,120 --> 00:19:31,080
I wonder if I can sleep for at least two hours.

286
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:37,820
Oh, it's Jin Sook.

287
00:19:37,820 --> 00:19:40,910
Why is she coming out from Soo Jin's house?

288
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:46,140
Hey. Be safe.

289
00:19:53,350 --> 00:19:58,130
Wait a minute... can you feel me too?

290
00:19:59,550 --> 00:20:02,520
I wonder if these kids have super powers or something.

291
00:20:12,110 --> 00:20:16,060
Goodnight, Mother and Father.

292
00:20:16,060 --> 00:20:19,580
By tomorrow, everything will be fine.

293
00:20:39,100 --> 00:20:41,090
There's no time for you to sleep now.

294
00:20:41,090 --> 00:20:43,100
You have to go keep an eye on Soo Jin.

295
00:20:43,100 --> 00:20:46,540
How come I always have to watch her when you get to sleep?

296
00:20:46,540 --> 00:20:49,460
- You were also the same a long time ago too! 
 - Ah, seriously!

297
00:20:49,460 --> 00:20:51,530
Hey, Soo Jin.

298
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:56,080
Where is she going this late at night?

299
00:20:59,090 --> 00:21:02,320
She should do some work on guarding her.

300
00:21:04,900 --> 00:21:07,400
Hey! Soo Jin, where are you going?

301
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:10,200
I'm asking you, where are you going?!

302
00:21:14,420 --> 00:21:16,020
Oh.

303
00:21:19,260 --> 00:21:22,420
It's you, isn't it? Pil, it's you, right?

304
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:24,980
Hey.

305
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:27,430
- It seems like she's able to feel something.
 - What was that?

306
00:21:27,430 --> 00:21:29,190
Wait a minute.

307
00:21:31,520 --> 00:21:33,540
I have to talk to her.

308
00:21:33,540 --> 00:21:35,890
Where are you?

309
00:21:36,470 --> 00:21:39,610
Oh, okay.

310
00:21:43,870 --> 00:21:45,830
Why aren't you sleeping?

311
00:21:45,830 --> 00:21:49,650
As a public servant, your body is not your own.

312
00:21:49,650 --> 00:21:53,540
Even if you can't fall asleep, you must do so because you have to do your job perfectly without a problem tomorrow.

313
00:21:53,540 --> 00:21:55,330
Get some sleep.

314
00:21:58,350 --> 00:22:03,590
Father, I wonder what happened to us last night.

315
00:22:05,370 --> 00:22:09,030
Something that we are not able to comprehend is happening to us.

316
00:22:09,030 --> 00:22:12,130
You have to be alert.

317
00:22:12,130 --> 00:22:15,460
While you maintain your inner peace.

318
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:24,830
How dare he embarrass me like that at the hospital where there are a lot of people.

319
00:22:24,830 --> 00:22:28,500
I will never forget the shame that Director Bong gave me.

320
00:22:28,500 --> 00:22:31,770
I will clear my name once and for all.

321
00:22:31,770 --> 00:22:34,620
Please do the same for me, Father.

322
00:22:34,700 --> 00:22:40,010
I will do that. Revenge is all about thirst. Bring me some water now.

323
00:22:40,010 --> 00:22:42,240
Okay, I will go get it.

324
00:23:03,030 --> 00:23:06,820
What the? Where is that punk going?

325
00:23:09,110 --> 00:23:10,860
I guess we ran out of water.

326
00:23:10,860 --> 00:23:15,520
No, that's not it. I remember boiling a kettle full of water last night.

327
00:23:25,030 --> 00:23:26,640
Seok Tae.

328
00:23:27,230 --> 00:23:31,520
- Where are you going?
-  I'm going to go meet Pil for a bit.

329
00:23:45,100 --> 00:23:48,400
You're Pil, right?

330
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:00,910
You...

331
00:24:02,950 --> 00:24:05,840
You're able to recognize me, right?

332
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:08,500
Soo Jin.

333
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:34,490
What is this picture?

334
00:24:40,020 --> 00:24:43,240
Hold on a minute. Hold on, hold on.

335
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:45,920
Are you even speaking Korean?

336
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:48,420
I can only speak Korean.

337
00:24:48,420 --> 00:24:52,010
I have no idea what you're saying to me right now.

338
00:24:52,010 --> 00:24:54,660
I have a hard time understanding that I'm talking to your soul right now.

339
00:24:54,660 --> 00:25:00,000
You getting hurt is all a fantasy too? So the past six years, all of it?

340
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,780
That's right.

341
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:08,830
So you went back and forth using that manhole near the tunnel?

342
00:25:08,830 --> 00:25:14,070
So you left at 12 o'clock midnight and came back at 12 o'clock in the afternoon?

343
00:25:15,590 --> 00:25:18,250
Hey, does that even make any sense?

344
00:25:18,250 --> 00:25:21,100
Are you Alice from  Alice in Wonderland  or something?

345
00:25:21,100 --> 00:25:25,210
For Alice, it's a rabbit hole. For me, it's a manhole.

346
00:25:29,520 --> 00:25:32,570
Hey, do you remember that?

347
00:25:32,570 --> 00:25:34,850
When we were kids, we used to sit on that bench.

348
00:25:34,850 --> 00:25:36,660
I don't remember.

349
00:25:38,610 --> 00:25:41,460
Think about it carefully. We—

350
00:25:41,460 --> 00:25:45,570
I don't remember. I don't remember. I'm telling you that I can't.

351
00:25:48,220 --> 00:25:52,160
So that never existed at all? I thought it did though.

352
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:56,100
- For instance, back when we were in the third grade—
 - No, I told you to stop!

353
00:25:59,790 --> 00:26:05,010
 Sitting here really makes me feel good. 

354
00:26:05,010 --> 00:26:08,540
 Other kids don't know about this place. I discovered it. 

355
00:26:08,540 --> 00:26:11,450
 - This spot belongs to you now.
 - Really? 

356
00:26:11,450 --> 00:26:15,660
 Of course! I won't let the other kids sit here. 

357
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:27,900
I told you to stop!

358
00:26:27,900 --> 00:26:30,570
So are you saying that never happened?

359
00:26:30,570 --> 00:26:33,560
It did happen! Then what about back in the third grade?

360
00:26:33,560 --> 00:26:37,840
Hey you! Do you even remember what picture you drew during art class that time?!

361
00:26:37,840 --> 00:26:39,470
The other kids made fun of me because of that...

362
00:26:39,470 --> 00:26:44,660
Back then, I thought that when a boy and a girl kiss, they are supposed to get married.

363
00:26:45,430 --> 00:26:48,130
Oh yeah? Fine then.

364
00:26:48,940 --> 00:26:52,060
- Let's get married.
 - Huh?

365
00:26:52,060 --> 00:26:56,280
You said that you'd be normal again after you're able to go back through that manhole.

366
00:26:56,280 --> 00:26:58,560
So let's get married.

367
00:27:07,700 --> 00:27:12,760
What would I be once you go back to normal again?

368
00:27:14,670 --> 00:27:16,630
Oh... oh.

369
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:22,810
Just... you'd be exactly the same.

370
00:27:23,940 --> 00:27:26,440
You'll be waiting for me too.

371
00:27:31,140 --> 00:27:33,510
You'll  also be preparing for the wedding as well.

372
00:27:39,460 --> 00:27:48,050
♫  Since love came and knocked on my heart  ♫

373
00:27:48,050 --> 00:27:50,990
My body feels so wobbly as if I'm drunk.

374
00:27:52,580 --> 00:27:54,960
You okay? You sleepy?

375
00:27:56,750 --> 00:27:58,430
You know that I can't stay awake when I'm sleepy, right?

376
00:27:58,430 --> 00:28:00,160
Of course I know.

377
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,740
Oh, hey.

378
00:28:01,740 --> 00:28:03,990
Get on my back. Get on my back.

379
00:28:03,990 --> 00:28:07,260
- I'm fine! 
- It's okay. Hurry and get on my back.

380
00:28:07,260 --> 00:28:10,290
I'm not going to wait too long for you.

381
00:28:11,080 --> 00:28:14,460
Alright! Here I go!

382
00:28:14,460 --> 00:28:23,130
♫   You are the so-called feeling. You are the small tremor  ♫

383
00:28:23,130 --> 00:28:27,500
♫   Because you are my half which  ♫

384
00:28:27,500 --> 00:28:31,790
♫   Fate gave to show affection for me  ♫

385
00:28:31,790 --> 00:28:36,440
♫   Because you are the feeling that is love, this tremor is good  ♫

386
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:41,780
I don't know how I can pour out my heart to you.

387
00:28:41,780 --> 00:28:48,270
I thought about you more than  three times a day everyday.

388
00:28:50,830 --> 00:28:52,910
People say...

389
00:28:55,090 --> 00:28:58,830
that this is love.

390
00:28:58,830 --> 00:29:02,840
♫   Secretly entering, come beside me and excite me more  ♫

391
00:29:02,840 --> 00:29:06,790
Are you listening to me?

392
00:29:06,790 --> 00:29:10,440
♫   My heart which is on the tip of my tongue confesses to you always  ♫

393
00:29:11,190 --> 00:29:16,250
Right. Every time I look for something to say, I'm never able to find anything.

394
00:29:16,250 --> 00:29:20,660
But now you are sleeping while I'm spilling out everything to you.

395
00:29:21,970 --> 00:29:24,170
I heard it all.

396
00:29:26,900 --> 00:29:29,310
I'm glad you heard it all.

397
00:29:29,310 --> 00:29:33,040
You'll probably forget it all once I go back through that manhole again.

398
00:29:34,370 --> 00:29:36,840
At least I can remember everything so that's a good thing.

399
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:40,520
♫  That's good  ♫

400
00:29:40,520 --> 00:29:44,530
Soo Jin, I have a favor to ask you.

401
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:50,530
If I don't go back to the manhole by 12 o'clock tonight,

402
00:29:52,370 --> 00:29:56,190
everything might disappear forever. So...

403
00:29:57,840 --> 00:30:00,660
You're being so loud.

404
00:30:01,690 --> 00:30:04,030
Oh, sorry.

405
00:30:04,690 --> 00:30:06,500
Are you sleeping?

406
00:30:17,280 --> 00:30:20,310
Seok Tae is carrying Soo Jin now?

407
00:30:21,560 --> 00:30:23,610
That's not possible.

408
00:30:24,710 --> 00:30:27,530
There's no way that Seok Tae is blessed with such a fine girl like that.

409
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:31,740
Who exactly are you?

410
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:39,600
- So tired.
 - You...You!

411
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:42,460
Father, where have you been?

412
00:30:42,460 --> 00:30:43,860
You told me to bring you water.

413
00:30:43,860 --> 00:30:45,330
I did indeed.

414
00:30:45,330 --> 00:30:49,520
Father, I went to go get water but the sun is up already.

415
00:30:49,520 --> 00:30:53,840
That's strange. Ah, I'm so tired.

416
00:30:57,630 --> 00:31:00,830
I guess he slipped out of there already.

417
00:31:23,710 --> 00:31:30,160
♫  If we are like each other  ♫

418
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:39,170
♫  We can feel each other  ♫

419
00:31:39,170 --> 00:31:45,660
♫  Now I know your pain  ♫

420
00:31:45,660 --> 00:31:49,980
♫  When I see your tears flow  ♫

421
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:58,170
♫  It feels like even my heart is ripping apart  ♫

422
00:31:58,170 --> 00:32:02,640
♫  Now both the pain  ♫

423
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:07,570
♫  And all the wounds  ♫

424
00:32:07,570 --> 00:32:15,150
♫  Everything which has distressed my heart  ♫

425
00:32:15,150 --> 00:32:23,140
♫  I want to entrust to you  ♫

426
00:32:23,140 --> 00:32:27,880
 I've waited for you for so long. 

427
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:35,550
♫  I am someone who believed I could live alone  ♫

428
00:32:36,550 --> 00:32:40,750
♫  Like a fool  ♫

429
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:02,120
What the?

430
00:33:02,120 --> 00:33:04,780
You crazy!? Why are you wearing jackets in this summer heat? Hurry up and take it off.

431
00:33:04,780 --> 00:33:06,560
I don't want to.

432
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:08,690
I don't want to either.

433
00:33:18,070 --> 00:33:20,870
Next time say that you want money instead.

434
00:33:20,870 --> 00:33:23,900
So they can bring some money with them instead of wearing those jackets.

435
00:33:23,900 --> 00:33:26,780
They are both bums.

436
00:33:26,780 --> 00:33:31,200
But how come you're only staring at one bum out of the two?

437
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:34,220
Because I like that one bum way better.

438
00:33:34,850 --> 00:33:37,210
- Alright!
 - It's shaking over here.

439
00:33:37,210 --> 00:33:39,570
I know what I'm doing man.

440
00:33:39,570 --> 00:33:41,810
You remember what I told you, right?

441
00:33:41,810 --> 00:33:44,210
Date someone who likes you.

442
00:33:44,210 --> 00:33:48,070
Otherwise, you have to stare at the back of a man for the rest of your life.

443
00:33:48,070 --> 00:33:54,370
You're saying that again. I'm not like you, Mom. You are not good at dating,

444
00:33:54,370 --> 00:33:56,100
but I'm not like that at all.

445
00:33:56,100 --> 00:33:58,780
Oh my.

446
00:34:01,690 --> 00:34:04,630
I'm so thirsty.

447
00:34:06,120 --> 00:34:08,350
Here's some water.

448
00:34:19,700 --> 00:34:21,730
Thanks.

449
00:34:25,040 --> 00:34:27,430
Wow, that's so refreshing.

450
00:34:31,950 --> 00:34:35,960
Seok Tae, what are you doing in front of my company anyway?

451
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:40,000
Jin Sook, someone told me that I met with Soo Jin last night.

452
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:42,790
Soo Jin?

453
00:34:42,790 --> 00:34:46,210
Wait a minute. If you met her, then you met her. But what's up with saying that someone told you about it, huh?

454
00:34:46,210 --> 00:34:49,640
I can't remember again.

455
00:34:49,640 --> 00:34:51,240
What are you talking about?

456
00:34:51,240 --> 00:34:54,810
So you met with Soo Jin last night but you can't remember at all?

457
00:34:54,810 --> 00:34:58,710
Yep, that's right.  But I was told that I was possessed by a ghost.

458
00:34:58,710 --> 00:35:02,230
I wonder why the ghost didn't take you away. What a shame, I must say.

459
00:35:02,230 --> 00:35:04,050
I'm not joking here. I'm being serious.

460
00:35:04,050 --> 00:35:08,320
My father followed me around and saw me dating with Soo Jin.

461
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:10,450
And he told me that I even gave Soo Jin a piggy back ride and stuff.

462
00:35:10,450 --> 00:35:12,900
At least your wish came true in your dreams.

463
00:35:12,900 --> 00:35:14,780
Didn't you have a crush on Soo Jin since a long time ago?

464
00:35:14,780 --> 00:35:17,850
No, not anymore. I gave up on Soo Jin a long time ago actually.

465
00:35:17,850 --> 00:35:22,140
You should know that you're the one I like now.

466
00:35:23,110 --> 00:35:26,230
- Ghost, please take him away. There's a crazy guy here. Crazy guy!
 - Hey!

467
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:28,130
Hey! I'm being serious here.

468
00:35:28,130 --> 00:35:31,410
I came to see you because I'm truly scared.

469
00:35:32,260 --> 00:35:34,990
What's up with all these kids?

470
00:35:34,990 --> 00:35:37,670
They are not playing with me like "Hidden Camera" (TV Show), either.

471
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:42,160
Jin Sook, you have a very strong spirit and energy.

472
00:35:42,160 --> 00:35:45,900
So you should protect me. Please?

473
00:35:45,900 --> 00:35:48,720
Do you think you can stay with me tonight?

474
00:35:48,720 --> 00:35:51,710
Wow...

475
00:35:51,710 --> 00:35:55,240
Are you hitting on me now using ghosts as an excuse out of all things?

476
00:35:55,240 --> 00:35:59,770
Seok Tae, you are such  a creative kid. You are amazing.

477
00:35:59,770 --> 00:36:02,900
Jin Sook, you know what's the most amazing thing?

478
00:36:02,900 --> 00:36:05,770
Soo Jin is constantly texting me now.

479
00:36:05,770 --> 00:36:08,230
She keeps on asking me if I'm Pil or not.

480
00:36:31,430 --> 00:36:34,690
I slept too much!

481
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:44,370
What the heck?

482
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:38,390
Hey, what took you so lo—

483
00:37:38,390 --> 00:37:41,820
I didn't expect that you were waiting for me, Soo Jin.

484
00:37:44,010 --> 00:37:47,080
I couldn't sleep at all last night.

485
00:37:48,130 --> 00:37:50,770
Yesterday was a strange day for me.

486
00:37:52,820 --> 00:37:55,590
Did anything happen to you yesterday, Soo Jin?

487
00:37:55,590 --> 00:37:59,330
I lost my memory after I came here to visit you.

488
00:37:59,330 --> 00:38:03,010
Did you drink yesterday?

489
00:38:03,010 --> 00:38:05,440
I don't drink alcohol.

490
00:38:06,260 --> 00:38:08,130
There's something strange about this.

491
00:38:08,130 --> 00:38:11,170
There is something that we can't quite comprehend.

