521
00:41:22,550 --> 00:41:24,550
While waiting for someone too.

522
00:41:28,040 --> 00:41:32,490
I'm sure someone will come for you and be by your side, Jae Hyeon.

523
00:41:33,530 --> 00:41:35,400
