534
00:42:50,330 --> 00:42:53,750
What did you do to make your soul suddenly so weak?

535
00:42:53,750 --> 00:42:57,670
Ahjussi, something is wrong with me.

536
00:42:57,670 --> 00:42:59,660
My body feels so weak, and Soo Jin can't even feel me.

537
00:42:59,660 --> 00:43:01,750
